    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS. This specimen delivers visceral performance through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory M-variable differential lock. The chassis is in exemplary state, with a verified reinforced rear subframe and pristine bushings ensuring optimal torsional rigidity. Finished in original Laguna Seca Blue with factory-spec tolerances maintained throughout the drivetrain, this vehicle represents a turn-key investment for the discerning purist seeking peak mechanical engagement.",
