    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a museum-quality 2002 BMW M3 Coupe, featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant and a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This specimen represents the pinnacle of atmospheric engineering, boasting individual throttle bodies and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis is impeccably preserved, with documented subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive double-VANOS overhaul already performed using Beisan components. Finished in Titanium Silver over Black Nappa leather, the exterior retains its deep factory luster with zero signs of oxidation or road rash. Every bushing, seal, and fluid is current, ensuring the hallmark E46 tactile feedback and telepathic turn-in. An uncompromising, turn-key example for the discerning collector.",
